WEBVTT

00:03:29.920 --> 00:03:32.160
(Laughter)

00:03:33.880 --> 00:03:36.656
His advice was so unexpected,

00:03:36.680 --> 00:03:37.936
when I got home,

00:03:37.960 --> 00:03:39.216
I turned on my computer

00:03:39.240 --> 00:03:42.720
and opened the folder
where I had saved all the hate mail.

00:03:43.760 --> 00:03:45.600
There were literally hundreds of them.

00:03:46.600 --> 00:03:51.056
Emails that started
with words like "terrorist,"

00:03:51.080 --> 00:03:52.696
"raghead,"

00:03:52.720 --> 00:03:54.200
"rat," "whore."

00:03:56.120 --> 00:03:59.600
I decided to contact the one
who had sent me the most.